{"id": "1424635801978802186", "channel_id": "1421974900742164500", "author_id": "183782216353054720", "author_name": "omnichromia", "content": "also, this is bothering the hell out of me. the Chapter 3 Resonance effects don't make sense, and I don't remember how it functioned before I unlocked all of these. \n\nStrange Pustule here describes that the Primary version of 「Mutated Heart」 discards your hand (X cards) then draws X+1 cards.\nDefiant Will's Lv.1 says it \"draws 1 more card\", and Lv.2 says it \"draws 2 more cards\", which insinuates that Lv.0 (inactivated) would draw N/A more cards, being the base X+1;\nSo if 「Mutated Heart」 with Defiant Will Lv.0 draws X+1 cards, then Lv.1 would draw X+2 cards, and Lv.3 would draw X+3 cards.\nBut Mutated Heart only draws a maximum of X+2 cards. Soooooo what's wrong here exactly? I feel like Strange Pustule is wrong, and that the Primary version of 「Mutated Heart」 actually draws X+0 cards, but I literally can't test that without making a new account and playing up until Chapter 3 to find out. <a:KleeREEE:816883329583808612>", "timestamp": "2025-10-06T05:54:03.645000+00:00", "thread_id": "1421974900742164500", "attachments": [{"id": "1424635801345458238", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/webp", "size": 268524, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1421974900742164500/1424635801345458238/image.png?ex=6a32367b&is=6a30e4fb&hm=7f6316ce406ac196a1130d4d9c4b56ded988f5491b44ce832d0bd9d09d6d7932&"}, {"id": "1424635801672876093", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/webp", "size": 224656, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1421974900742164500/1424635801672876093/image.png?ex=6a32367b&is=6a30e4fb&hm=6179115d3d005931eb46f7727536fd91696c19e07023fca281db3dced7a9d0fd&"}]}
